<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="117" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1436,151,429]" pageId="12" pageNumber="117">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,331,357]" pageId="12" pageNumber="117">Etymology.</emphasis>
We name this subspecies in honor of Gustavo Suárez, expert ornithologist and dedicated conservationist who collected the first known specimen, and whose tragic death by criminal hands in 
<date box="[1286,1436,367,393]" pageId="12" pageNumber="117" value="2017-01">January 2017</date>
cut short a promising conservation career.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
